{"tid":1449712,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"8月12日 全民黑衣眼罩日","createTime":"2019-08-11T17:01:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T17:55:38.000Z","uid":168391,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f72878a06ca0d5306a026ef7d1c61f06f2219195","tid":1449712,"uid":168391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:01:56.000Z","msg":"今日嘅事 無須多講<br />\n幾個鐘之後 無論大家做咩<br />\n唔該大家帶咁黑 著咁黑<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>悼念六位英魂烈士 尤其係本來光明嘅前程<br />\n哀悼諸位受傷勇士 尤其係今日失明嘅少女<br />\n銘記眾位正受牢獄之災嘅賢達</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>表達我哋對政府賣港嘅不滿<br />\n怒吼我哋對警察濫暴嘅憤慨</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">叫喊我哋對五大訴求嘅渴望<br />\n高呼我哋對光復香港嘅希冀</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"238dbbc672130f0797e166f69a1717efbfb9d4b2","tid":1449712,"uid":168391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:02:31.000Z","msg":"聽日有好多行動 但做咩都好 全黑please!"},{"pid":"5d5fd3fe2e5792b134eac2a79d1369b1770edba9","tid":1449712,"uid":168391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:04:00.000Z","msg":"光復香港<br />\n時代革命"},{"pid":"eb39de8ee7405c8dd9828d55b5662b4d0f34c57d","tid":1449712,"uid":168391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:04:51.000Z","msg":"五大訴求<br />\n缺一不可"},{"pid":"e238c014635dc796e2f4d044283983d9b911318e","tid":1449712,"uid":168391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:05:03.000Z","msg":"悼念六位英魂烈士 尤其係本來光明嘅前程"},{"pid":"47b072e6f7f74cf190ab8e118e007041bc9d7d8c","tid":1449712,"uid":168391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:05:16.000Z","msg":"哀悼諸位受傷勇士 尤其係今日失明嘅少女"},{"pid":"ac5182738b37a4dfd19764aabe0db7d6e75fe688","tid":1449712,"uid":168391,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T17:05:31.000Z","msg":"銘記眾位正受牢獄之災嘅賢